org.qiweb.api

Interface BuildVersion


  • public interface BuildVersion
    Generated class that store the version derived from the build system.

    • Field Summary

      Fields  
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String COMMIT
      The last commit hash from the git history, that is 3b58cf2.
      static String DATE
      The date this file was generated, usually the last date that the project was modified, that is Thu, 27 Nov 2014 18:38:13 GMT.
      static String DETAILED_VERSION
      The full details of the version, including the build date, that is org.qiweb:org.qiweb.api:0.4.0 3b58cf2 Thu, 27 Nov 2014 18:38:13 GMT.
      static boolean DIRTY
      True if they were local changes when built, that is false.
      static String GROUP
      The group of the project from the gradle build, that is org.qiweb.
      static String NAME
      The name of the project from the gradle build, that is org.qiweb.api.
      static String VERSION
      The version of the project from the gradle build, that is 0.4.0.
